### Project Title:WKLAssesment
Assignment

###Prerequisites:
Have java ,Testng,apache.commons.io,chrome exe installed

###Technology Used : Java, TestNG framework, Selenium.

###Features:The project consist of 3 packages:
1.beforeSuite:
SeleniumHelper initilazes driver(Of your choice:currently chrome)
2.businesscomponent:

Element class:Has all methods required to perform basic actions(Eg:click,gettext,submit)
elementSelector:Has all methods by which we can select particular element(byName/byXPath)
ExecutionLogic:Includes required methods to check Offer functionality(emptyCart/searchProduct/addToCart/checkPrice)
Listeners:For reporting
SeleniumHelper:Browser selection

3.businessSuite
ShoppingBol lass:Has complete functionality check by calling required methods in sequence manner
Currently targeted product is "Google Chromecast - Media Streamer".

###How to use:
Enter credentilas of your and change parameter name="Path"(where chrome exe is stored )
Same Path parameter is used to store screenshot when script fails

###Results:
Also diffrent formats are available in test output folder(html,emailabe)
